name: INTO THE BULLET HELL
description:
YOUR NAME IS TRACY.  YOU'RE HERE TO KILL THE DEVIL.

INTO THE BULLET HELL is a nightmarish wave-based action game.  Assume the role of TRACY ( who is really good at KICKING, and is in HELL, KICKING DEMONS ) and KICK DEMONS in HELL. 

Created in under 100 hours for the 5TH EXTRA CREDITS GAME JAM.

HELL YEAH.
